Summary: String manipulation for cosmetic and programming application
Version: %{tl_version}
Release: %{tl_noarch_release}.1.20.svn17906%{?dist}
BuildArch: noarch
Requires: texlive-base = %{tl_version}
Requires: texlive-kpathsea-bin = %{tl_version}
